I"p<p>Bean Boy Games is an indie video game company I founded with two of my best friends when I was 17 years old. Since then, we’ve released four video games on Steam: a 2D puzzle platformer and three virtual reality games. We’re always working on new games together.</p>

<h3 id="turner">Turner</h3>
<p>Turner is a 2D platformer puzzle game where you take the role of Turner, a man with a troubled past and an unstable state of mind. Traverse hundreds of levels in an asylum by rotating the world around you, all while trying to solve the mystery of why you’re there.</p>

<p>Key Features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Rotate the world at your will to make your way through the asylum and uncover the secrets of your past</li>
  <li>Learn new abilities and utilize the tools around you to solve puzzles and avoid hazards</li>
  <li>250+ original levels, 250+ challenge levels</li>
  <li>Original dark themed “sketch style” art</li>
  <li>Original soundtrack</li>
  <li>Full Controller support</li>
  <li>Speedrun mode</li>
</ul>

